{"type":"message","id":"42779f51","parentId":"f9ee0036","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:24:45.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me write today's memory note about this:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-841813f2066c129a","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-29.md","content":"# Memory - 2026-03-29\n\n## Notion Integration Setup\n- Found Notion API key in `.env` file: `NOTION_KEY=ntn_...`\n- Created Python scripts for Notion automation:\n  - `check_notion.py` - Read and display page structure\n  - `add_visuals.py` - Add visual elements (callouts, progress)\n  - `visual_overhaul.py` - Comprehensive visual upgrade\n  - `add_icons.py` - Add emoji icons to todo items\n  - `update_progress.py` - Dynamic progress bar calculator\n  - `notion_progress.sh` - Quick shell command to update progress\n\n## Visual Enhancements Applied\n- Color-coded sections: Daily (green), Monthly (blue), Yearly (orange)\n- Custom icons for each task (🎯🔨📝🔍🚫🚀🧠💰🧹💸📁🏗️👥💪)\n- Today's Focus toggle with collapsible tips\n- Motivational callout with blue background\n- Visual key/legend for priorities\n- Dynamic progress bar (updates based on completed todos)\n\n## Progress Bar Feature\n- Fully functional - counts total todos and completed\n- Updates percentage and visual bar\n- Color changes based on progress: <40% default, 40-70% yellow, 70%+ green\n- Can be refreshed anytime by running: `python3 update_progress.py` or `./notion_progress.sh`\n\n## User Context\n- Ivek wants visually appealing Notion workspace\n- Has 14 todos across Daily/Monthly/Yearly sections\n- Currently 0% complete (fresh start)\n- Likes actionable, functional features\n\n## Next Steps Ideas\n- Add cover image to Notion page\n- Add page icon\n- Create database view for todos\n- Add automation to run progress update on schedule"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":29485,"output":426,"cacheRe