{"type":"message","id":"cf6e71ab","parentId":"bae58ca5","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:29:19.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ **DONE! Your Todo List is Now LIVE!**\n\nI've converted your simple checkboxes into a **proper Notion database** with instant progress updates. Here's what you have:\n\n### **📊 New Database Features:**\n| Property | Options |\n|----------|---------|\n| **Task** | All 14 todos migrated |\n| **Status** | 📋 Not Started → 🔄 In Progress → ✅ Done |\n| **Priority** | 🔴 High / 🟡 Medium / 🟢 Low |\n| **Timeframe** | 📅 Daily / 📆 Monthly / 🎯 Yearly |\n| **Progress** | **LIVE FORMULA** (0% → 50% → 100%) |\n\n### **⚡ How It Works:**\n1. Open your Notion page\n2. Find the **\"✅ Task Tracker\"** database (scroll down)\n3. Change any task's Status to **\"✅ Done\"**\n4. **Progress column updates INSTANTLY** — no scripts, no refresh needed\n\n### **🎨 Recommended: Create These Views**\nIn Notion, click \"+ New View\" on the database:\n1. **Board View** → Group by \"Status\" (Kanban board)\n2. **Board View** → Group by \"Timeframe\" (Daily/Monthly/Yearly)\n3. **List View** → Sort by \"Priority\" (High on top)\n\n---\n\n**🔥 Go check it out!** Change a task status and watch progress update in real-time. No more running scripts — it just works."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":35230,"output":328,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35558,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774744150305,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8b13c7a8a9b5a50a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9cf83184","parentId":"cf6e71ab","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:30:15.609Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"261\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6735239700\",\n  \"sender\": \"Ivek\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 01:30 GMT+1\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Ivek (6735239700)\",\n  \"id\": \"6735239700\",\n  \"name\": \"Ivek\"\n}\n```\n\nmake everything on one page and clean up the visuals also the content"}],"timestamp":1774744215604}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bca933b","parentId":"9cf83184","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:32:25.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Got it. Let me clean up the page — remove the old checkbox todos, keep the database, organize everything nicely on one clean page. I'll delete the old blocks and restructure."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-9dd3abad9526092b","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/cleanup_page.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nClean up Notion page - remove old todos, organize everything cleanly\n\"\"\"\nimport requests\n\nNOTION_KEY = \"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\"\nPAGE_ID = \"331996240a6680268f4bc68282b2bba6\"\n\nheaders = {\n    \"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {NOTION_KEY}\",\n    \"Notion-Version\": \"2022-06-28\",\n    \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"\n}\n\ndef get_all_blocks():\n    \"\"\"Get all blocks on the page\"\"\"\n    url = f\"https://api.notion.com/v1/blocks/{PAGE_ID}/children\"\n    response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)\n    return response.json().get('results', [])\n\ndef delete_block(block_id):\n    \"\"\"Delete a single block\"\"\"\n    url = f\"https://api.notion.com/v1/blocks/{block_id}\"\n    response = requests.delete(url, headers=headers)\n    return response.status_code == 200\n\ndef delete_old_todos():\n    \"\"\"Delete all old checkbox todos and related blocks, keep database\"\"\"\n    print(\"🧹 Cleaning up old content...\")\n    \n    blocks = get_all_blocks()\n    deleted = 0\n    \n    # Types to delete: to_do, heading_2 (old sections), divider, paragraph, callout, toggle\n    # Keep: database (child_database, child_page)\n    types_to_delete = ['to_do', 'heading_1', 'heading_2', 'heading_3', 'divider', 'paragraph', 'callout', 'toggle', 'quote']\n    \n    for block in blocks:\n        block_type = block.get('type')\n        \n        # Skip databases\n        if block_type in ['child_database', 'child_page']:\n            print(f\"   ⏭️  Keeping: {block_type}\")\n            continue\n        \n        # Delete everything else\n        if block_type in types_to_delete:\n            if delete_block(block['id']):\n                deleted += 1\n                print(f\"   🗑️  Deleted: {block_type}\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\n✅ Deleted {deleted} old blocks\")\n\ndef add_clean_structure():\n    \"\"\"Add clean, minimal structure\"\"\"\n    print(\"\\n✨ Adding clean structure...\")\n    \n    # Add clean header and instructions\n    clean_data = {\n        \"children\": [\n            # Title\n            {\n                \"object\": \"block\",\n                \"type\": \"heading_1\",\n                \"heading_1\": {\n                    \"rich_text\": [{\n                        \"type\": \"text\",\n                        \"text\": {\"content\": \"🎯 Ivek's Goals\"},\n                        \"annotations\": {\"bold\": True, \"color\": \"blue\"}\n                    }]\n                }\n            },\n            # Simple instruction\n            {\n                \"object\": \"block\",\n                \"type\": \"callout\",\n                \"callout\": {\n                    \"rich_text\": [{\n                        \"type\": \"text\",\n                        \"text\": {\"content\": \"Change task Status to Done → Progress updates instantly\"}\n                    }],\n                    \"icon\": {\"emoji\": \"⚡\"},\n                    \"color\": \"gray_background\"\n                }\n            },\n            # Divider\n            {\n                \"object\": \"block\",\n                \"type\": \"divider\",\n                \"divider\": {}\n            }\n        ]\n    }\n    \n    url = f\"https://api.notion.com/v1/blocks/{PAGE_ID}/children\"\n    response = requests.patch(url, headers=headers, json=clean_data)\n    \n    if response.status_code == 200:\n        print(\"✅ Clean structure added!\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"❌ Failed: {response.status_code}\")\n\ndef verify_database():\n    \"\"\"Verify the database still exists\"\"\"\n    print(\"\\n📋 Checking database...\")\n    blocks = get_all_blocks()\n    \n    for block in blocks:\n        if block.get('type') == 'child_database':\n            print(f\"✅ Database found: {block.get('child_database', {}).get('database_id', 'unknown')}\")\n            return True\n    \n    print(\"⚠️  No database found!\")\n    return False\n\ndef main():\n    print(\"=\" * 50)\n    print(\"🧹 CLEANING UP NOTION PAGE\")\n    print(\"=\" * 50)\n    \n    # Delete old content\n    delete_old_todos()\n    \n    # Add clean structure\n    add_clean_structure()\n    \n    # Verify database exists\n    verify_database()\n    \n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 50)\n    print(\"✨ CLEANUP COMPLETE!\")\n    print(\"=\" * 50)\n    print(\"\\nYour page now has:\")\n    print(\"  • Clean title\")\n    print(\"  • Simple instruction callout\")\n    print(\"  • Task Tracker database (with all your tasks)\")\n    print(\"\\n🔥 Open Notion to see the clean layout!\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":35681,"output":1092,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36773,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774744215615,"responseId":"chatcmpl-969210e3cf15aef2"}}
