{"type":"message","id":"0314445b","parentId":"daaeff85","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:42:55.764Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-be736836fe30313f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Memory - 2026-03-29\n\n## 🔑 API Keys & Secrets Rule\n**ALWAYS check `.env` file first** when API keys or secrets are needed.\n- Location: `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/.env`\n- Ivek stores credentials there (e.g., `NOTION_KEY=ntn_...`)\n- Don't ask for keys — check `.env` first\n\n## Notion Integration Setup\n- Found Notion API key in `.env` file: `NOTION_KEY=ntn_...`\n- Created Python scripts for Notion automation:\n  - `check_notion.py` - Read and display page structure\n  - `add_visuals.py` - Add visual elements (callouts, progress)\n  - `visual_overhaul.py` - Comprehensive visual upgrade\n  - `add_icons.py` - Add emoji icons to todo items\n  - `update_progress.py` - Dynamic progress bar calculator\n  - `notion_progress.sh` - Quick shell command to update progress\n\n## Visual Enhancements Applied\n- Color-coded sections: Daily (green), Monthly (blue), Yearly (orange)\n- Custom icons for each task (🎯🔨📝🔍🚫🚀🧠💰🧹💸📁🏗️👥💪)\n- Today's Focus toggle with collapsible tips\n- Motivational callout with blue background\n- Visual key/legend for priorities\n- Dynamic progress bar (updates based on completed todos)\n\n## Progress Bar Feature\n- Fully functional - counts total todos and completed\n- Updates percentage and visual bar\n- Color changes based on progress: <40% default, 40-70% yellow, 70%+ green\n- Can be refreshed anytime by running: `python3 update_progress.py` or `./notion_progress.sh`\n\n## User Context\n- Ivek wants visually appealing Notion workspace\n- Has 14 todos across Daily/Monthly/Yearly sections\n- Currently 0% complete (fresh start)\n- Likes actionable, functional features\n\n## Database Conversion (Live Progress)\n- Converted checkbox todos to proper Notion database\n- Database ID: `33299624-0a66-818e-92d0-dabaca1c1ec8`\n- Properties: Task, Status, Priority, Timeframe, Progress (formula)\n- Status options: 📋 Not Started, 🔄 In Progress, ✅ Done, ⏸️ Paused\n- Priority options: 🔴 High, 🟡 Medium, 🟢 Low\n- Timeframe options: 📅 Daily, 📆 Monthly, 🎯 Yearly\n- Progress formula: Not Started=0%, In Progress=50%, Done=100%\n- LIVE updates - no script needed, changes reflect instantly\n\n## Page Cleanup\n- Removed all old checkbox todos (38 blocks deleted)\n- Clean page structure: Title → Callout → Divider → Database\n- Notion API appends at end, so drag blocks in UI to reorder\n- Database contains all 14 tasks with live progress formula\n\n## Scripts Created\n- `create_database.py` - Converts todos to database with all properties\n- `add_dashboard.py` - Adds dashboard section with instructions\n- `cleanup_page.py` - Removes old content, keeps database\n- `rebuild_clean.py` - Final clean rebuild\n- All 14 tasks migrated with proper categorization"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774744975762}}
