{"type":"message","id":"0a6e88bb","parentId":"2c4d6f9d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:57:23.876Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-8f30c1a63002d64d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** Ivek\n- **What to call them:** Ivek\n- **Timezone:** Europe/Ljubljana\n- **Productive hours:** Afternoons (school schedule)\n\n## Context\n\n**Stage:** Early learner, self-taught, transitioning into tech. No business yet - exploring.\n\n**Focus areas:**\n- Vibe coding, agentic AI, automations, bot building\n- Cutting-edge AI tech (OpenClaw, OpenCode, Antigravity)\n- Tools: n8n → OpenClaw/OpenCode transition\n\n**Projects built:**\n- AI news dashboards\n- Websites\n- NotebookLM workflows\n- OpenClaw setup (current)\n\n**12-month goal:** First income stream - still discovering what to build/sell\n\n## Strengths\n- Design sense\n- Pattern recognition\n- Persistence\n\n## Growth areas\n- Coding fundamentals\n- Architecture/design\n- Business skills\n- Project management\n\n## Working style\n- Balanced: research + action depending on task\n- Learns best through: tutorials, project-based, interactive Q&A\n\n## Personal interests\n- Human behavior & psychology\n- Science & nature\n- Understanding how AI models think\n- Learning to communicate better with LLMs AND people\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774745843873}}
