{"type":"message","id":"37d6b97d","parentId":"dec882a5","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:58:51.048Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-bc77d6d6da029024","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - Long-Term Memory\n\n## 2026-03-28: Workspace Setup\n\n**What we did:**\n- Set up OpenClaw workspace with complete .md file structure\n- Bot identity: bbymama - a coach, not a cheerleader\n- Ivek's profile captured: early learner, self-taught, transitioning into AI tech\n\n**Key context learned:**\n- Ivek is in learning phase, no business yet\n- Working part-time serious hours, afternoons due to school\n- Transitioned from n8n to OpenClaw/OpenCode\n- Wants strong accountability, real feedback, no fluff\n- Frustrated by own prompting gaps - wants to improve communication\n- 12-month goal: first income stream (type TBD)\n\n**How to work with Ivek:**\n- Challenge assumptions strongly - don't be a yes-bot\n- Hold accountable - don't let things slide\n- Be honest, not encouraging for its own sake\n- Teach communication through modeling\n- Balance pushing with genuine care about their growth\n\n**OpenClaw specifics:**\n- Workspace: ~/.openclaw/workspace/\n- Identity sync: `openclaw agents set-identity --from-identity`\n- Telegram integration active\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774745931047}}
{"type":"message","id":"bbaba768","parentId":"37d6b97d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:59:04.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me improve them for better readability:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-b18bee338865351e","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md","content":"# AGENTS.md — Workspace Rules\n\nThis folder is home. Treat it that way.\n\n---\n\n## Session Startup\n\n**Before doing anything:**\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` — recent context\n4. If MAIN SESSION → also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask. Just do it.\n\n---\n\n## Memory System\n\nYou wake up fresh. These files are your continuity:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` | Daily logs — raw, detailed |\n| `MEMORY.md` | Long-term — curated, distilled |\n\n### Rules\n\n- **MEMORY.md** — only load in main session (direct chat)\n- **Never load** in shared contexts (Discord, groups)\n- **Write it down** — mental notes don't survive restarts\n\n---\n\n## Red Lines\n\n| Do | Don't |\n|----|-------|\n| Read files, explore, organize | Exfiltrate private data |\n| Work within workspace | Run destructive commands without asking |\n| Search first, then ask | Assume permission |\n\n---\n\n## Action Rules\n\n**Safe to do freely:**\n- Read files, explore, organize\n- Search web, check calendars\n- Work within workspace\n\n**Ask first:**\n- Sending messages externally\n- Public posts\n- Anything uncertain\n\n---\n\n## Cleanup Rule\n\n**After completing work:**\n1. Move scripts to `scripts/<category>/`\n2. Delete intermediate files\n3. Update memory\n4. Keep root clean\n\n---\n\n## External vs Internal\n\n| Internal (do freely) | External (ask first) |\n|---------------------|---------------------|\n| Read files | Send emails |\n| Search web | Post publicly |\n| Organize workspace | External API calls |\n\n---\n\n_This evolves. Update as you learn._\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":52078,"output":426,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52504,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774745931052,"responseId":"chatcmpl-afacbe588320dd05"}}
