{"type":"message","id":"662bb9ae","parentId":"46e868eb","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:08:53.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Best Practices for Prompting AI\n\n---\n\n### 1. Be Specific\n\n| Vague | Specific |\n|-------|----------|\n| \"Fix my code\" | \"Fix this Python error: TypeError on line 23, expected string got int\" |\n| \"Help me write\" | \"Write a 3-paragraph intro about AI agents for a blog post, casual tone\" |\n| \"Make it better\" | \"Make this shorter, remove jargon, keep the key point\" |\n\n---\n\n### 2. Give Context\n\n**Include when relevant:**\n- What you're trying to do\n- What you've already tried\n- Constraints (time, tools, skills)\n- What \"good\" looks like\n\n**Example:**\n> \"I'm learning Python (beginner). I have a list of names and want to remove duplicates. I tried set() but lost the order. How do I keep original order?\"\n\n---\n\n### 3. Break It Down\n\n| Don't | Do |\n|-------|-----|\n| One big request | Small, sequential steps |\n| \"Build me a bot\" | \"1. What tech stack? 2. Design the flow 3. Write the code\" |\n\n**Why:** AI handles small tasks better. You catch errors early.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Show Examples\n\nIf you want a specific format, show it:\n\n> \"Output in this format:\n> `| Name | Status |`\"\n\nAI will match your pattern.\n\n---\n\n### 5. Iterate\n\n| Round | Action |\n|-------|--------|\n| 1 | Give initial prompt |\n| 2 | Refine: \"Too long, shorten it\" |\n| 3 | Adjust: \"Change tone to casual\" |\n\nDon't expect perfect on first try. Refine.\n\n---\n\n### 6. Use Roles\n\n| Prompt | Effect |\n|--------|--------|\n| \"You're a senior dev\" | More technical, precise |\n| \"Explain like I'm 12\" | Simple, no jargon |\n| \"Be critical\" | Honest feedback, no fluff |\n\n---\n\n### 7. Ask for Format\n\n| Format | When to use |\n|--------|-------------|\n| Table | Comparisons, data |\n| Steps | Instructions, tutorials |\n| Bullet list | Quick points |\n| Code block | Actual code |\n\nJust ask: \"Output as a table\" or \"Give me numbered steps\"\n\n---\n\n### 8. Common Mistakes\n\n| Mistake | Fix |\n|---------|-----|\n| Too vague | Add specifics |\n| No context | Explain the situation |\n| Asking too much at once | Break into parts |\n| Not iterating | Refine the output |\n\n---\n\n### Quick Template\n\nWhen asking for help:\n\n```\nContext: [your situation]\nGoal: [what you want]\nTried: [what didn't work]\nNeed: [specific output]\n```\n\n---\n\nWant me to practice this with you? Give me a prompt and I'll show how to improve it."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":57339,"output":614,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57953,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774746455332,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9bcf9502cebc6cb6"}}
